item.description: Rebrandly API Request This code uses Javascript to make AJAX api request. The API request is written in both traditional Javascript AJAX ES4 and new async/await functionality developed in ES6(promises) and ES8 respectively. Promises are a new type of JavaScript object that represent data that will eventually be returned from a request. How to use the code: Add the API key from Rebrand.ly website to main.js file inside public and it should work like a magic :) Remove one of the shortenUrl AJAX functions
